[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 4.58,
    "text": "I would like to address something that I've been having to deal with for quite some time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.58,
    "endTime": 11.399000000000001,
    "text": "This is an issue that I face on an almost daily basis, and this week I've had to deal with it even more because we're in New York."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.4,
    "endTime": 16.95,
    "text": "People frequently confuse me with someone else, with another person who-- a person who isn't me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.95,
    "endTime": 26.61,
    "text": "And so as a public service to me, and to the other person, I got in touch with him, and we made a video together that hopefully will clear this little headache up once and for all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.61,
    "endTime": 28.59,
    "text": "Hi, I'm Jimmy Kimmel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.59,
    "endTime": 30.4,
    "text": "And I'm Jimmy Fallon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.4,
    "endTime": 33.42,
