  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.42,
    "endTime": 35.760000000000005,
    "text": "And some people think I'm Jimmy Fallon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.76,
    "endTime": 38.67,
    "text": "And it's causing a lot of problems for us at the airport."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.67,
    "endTime": 43.126000000000005,
    "text": "So we decided to make a quick video to explain who's who and what's what."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.93,
